        <h1>One disciplined standard, applied as far across your world as you need.</h1>
        <p class="sub">Every engagement applies the same government-grade hardening standard, in person, in your presence. What changes between tiers is reach — never the quality of the work. Here is exactly what that standard covers.</p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
            <a class="btn" href="#contact">Book a Threat Assessment</a>
